Package prisonescape.game.model.actors

Interface Summary
MapActor A simplified representation of an Actor in the assumed TiledMap.
 

Class Summary
Actor This class encapsulates the logic of an Actor within the game.
ActorAction This class specifies the methods required for a NPC within the game, which allow for it to behave in its own way.
GuardChasingBehaviour This class encapsulates the logic of a Guard who is chasing an Actor within the game.
Item This class encapsulates the logic of an Item within the game.
LimitedWalkingAction This class encapsulates the logic of an NPC who is appearing to move around in the environment.
 

Enum Summary
Actor.ACTOR_STATE This enum holds each of the states an Actor can have.
DIRECTION This class models each DIRECTION and their associated values.
Item.ITEM_TYPE An enum to store the different types of item which are available within the game.
